rows.label: tlk45100121_03_msg0001
rows.name:
Even after our bug-catching showdown,
me and Leif have been facing off
at all sorts of other things!

rows.label: tlk45100121_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Though we don't go anywhere near
dangerous places any more, of course.

rows.label: tlk45100121_03_msg0003
rows.name:
Anyway, at the moment I've
won ten times out of ten!
I haven't lost once!

rows.label: tlk45100121_03_msg0004
rows.name:
Yeah! I guess I really am my mam's
son. I don't believe in losing!
